nstructions about about--training\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text\">\n          <header class=\"block__header\">\n            <h2 class=\"block__heading\">For Students</h2>\n            <p>\n              To make sure you're fully prepared for each shift, Shiftly\n              strongly recommends students to complete a short training video\n              created by the restaurant prior to the shift. That way, you can\n              walk in confident and ready to get started with no extra training\n              needed on-site.\n            </p>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">1. watch the video</h3>\n            <p>Each restaurant provides a quick video that explains:</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                What your job will be (ex: dishwashing, bussing, hosting)\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">Where to go and who to check in with</li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                How the space is set up (kitchen layout, cleaning supplies,\n                etc.)\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Any key rules or expectations unique to that restaurant\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">2. confirm you understand</h3>\n            <p>\n              After watching the video, you'll simply press “Yes, I understand”\n              to confirm you're ready for the shift. It takes just a second.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">3. get verified</h3>\n            <p>\n              Once you complete the training, your profile will be marked as\n              \"Training Verified,\" which shows restaurants that you're\n              shift-ready.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--light block--instructions about about--training\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text\">\n          <header class=\"block__header\">\n            <h2 class=\"block__heading\">For Businesses</h2>\n            <p>\n              We know your time is limited–and training new workers for just one\n              shift can be frustrating. That's why Shiftly lets you create a\n              short, role-specific training video that students are strongly\n              recommended to watch before their shift.\n            </p>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">1. record a quick training video</h3>\n            <p>Film a short video (even on your phone) that walks through:</p>\n            <ul class=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                What the shift involves (e.g. dishwashing, bussing, hosting)\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Where to enter and who to check in with\n              </li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">Where supplies are and how to use them</li>\n              <li class=\"list__item\">\n                Any specific do's and don'ts you want them to know\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>\n              Most videos are 2-4 minutes long and help eliminate repetitive\n              explanations.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">2. upload & tag by role</h3>\n            <p>\n              Once the video is uploaded and linked to a specific role (e.g.\n              \"Dishwasher: Fridays\"), any student applying for that shift is\n              strongly recommended to watch it before they can be confirmed.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"block__paragraph\">\n            <h3 class=\"block__sub-heading\">\n              3. student confirms understanding\n            </h3>\n            <p>\n              After watching the video, students click a simple “Yes, I\n              understand” button to confirm. Their profile will show they’ve\n              completed your training, so you can skip the orientation and jump\n              right in.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"block block--dark block--bottom\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"block__text students\">\n          <header class=\"column__header\">\n            <h4 class=\"column_heading\">Students</h4>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"list\">\n            <a href=\"/a06f72b3e226a32ee6e99456d3af971a.html\">How it Works</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">FAQs</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Tips for Getting Hired</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Payment & Earnings</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Support</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"block__text students\">\n          <header class=\"column__header\">\n            <h4 class=\"column_heading\">Businesses</h4>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"list\">\n            <a href=\"/7c8ecc07dc451a2819ca7688b912cf29.html\">How it Works</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">FAQs</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Pricing & Fees</a>\n            <a href=\"/b6ae2fbbb3871a11238b1eb15d3a4c5f.html\">Advice for Job Posting</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"block__text students\">\n          <header class=\"column__header\">\n            <h4 class=\"column_heading\">Account</h4>\n          </header>\n